Details: Lodha Imperia is a residential project in Bhandup West, Mumbai. The residential project has 2 and 3BHK flats that are being resold and hence, ready for possession. There are 168 units in the complex, each measuring from 1233 to 1683 sq. ft. quite a few amenities are there for home owners to enjoy such as swimming pool, gymnasium, multipurpose room and video door phones for ensuring the security of home owners. Founded in 1980, the Lodha Group has worked on fifty four projects and counted among the top developers of Mumbai. They have thirty properties under construction currently. Some of their projects in the city are situated in Dombivali and Thane West.

Vikhroli region of Mumbai is one of the popular areas because of the real estate projects. One of them is the Sterling Park Residency project which offers a range of apartments in varying sizes and plans to suit the needs and budgets of different buyers. The region where this apartment is available is well surrounded by restaurant, bus station, ATM, bank, train station, park, school, petrol pump, hospital, etc. The different amenities offered by this project are a gym, a club house, a multipurpose room, and playground for children, 24 hours security, a power back up system and much more. The cost of the apartments is depended on the request value.

Lodha Casa Bella, located in Dombivali, Mumbai, offers 1,2 and 3 BHK apartments, with the price being on request. Splendour by Mahindra Lifespace, located in Bhandup West, Mumbai, offers 2 and 3 BHK apartments, with the price being on request. There are 487 units in total, and the apartment sizes range from 1486 to 1624sq. ft. The amenities include gymnasium, swimming pool, children’s play area, club house, jogging track, landscaped gardens, meditation area, party lawn, amphitheatre, and tennis court. Situated in suburb central Mumbai, Bhandup West is one of the popular localities, with the neighboring areas being Powai, Matunga, Kanjurmarg, Vikhroli etc. The major builders who have real estate projects here include Kamla, Marathon, Kalpataru, Neumec, HDIL, Neptune, Lodha, Aaditya Realtors and a few others. The average price of apartments here is 11540 per sq. ft.

Gurukripa Dhruv Heights is situated in close proximity to the Khargar railway station. The project is linked to both national and state highways which link it to various parts of Mumbai. The project comprises of 30 units with sizes ranging between 1250 and 1625 sq ft on an average. 2 and 3 BHK apartments are offered with amenities including power backup, indoor game facilities, a well-equipped gymnasium, intercom facilities, club house and playing area for children, 24 hour security and firefighting system. The area is in close proximity to the Central Business District housed in Belapur. This rapidly developing locality is located near the Taloja Industrial area. Several areas such as Vashi, Navi Mumbai, Kamothe and Kalamboli Link Road are accessible from the project through the Expressway that connect Panvel and Sion. Bus transport services are also available in the area and link it to Thane, Panvel, Uran, Dombivli and Khopoli.

Kalpataru Aura is a housing project in Ghatkopar West, Mumbai. The complex has 1224 units measuring between 1143 and 1360 sq. ft. These apartments can be moved into immediately and are being resold. They are of 2BHK configuration. Flat owners shall enjoy facilities such as massage and sauna room, half basketball court, garbage chute, basketball and badminton court. Kalpataru Group was founded in 1969 and has since then supervised the development of seventy four properties. Fifteen projects of theirs are under construction. Apart from Ghatkopar, their properties are in Thane West and Parel. Ghatkopar is an eastern suburb which has gained traction in the realty market with the commencement of the Versova Andheri Ghatkopar metro railway. It is connected to other parts of Mumbai via the Eastern Express Highway.

Aarsh Avenue Mumbai is a residential project developed by Aarsh Group. It is located at Badlapur West in Mumbai. Lodha Heaven is a housing complex in Dombivali, near Mumbai. The complex has 1, 2 and 3 BHK flats on offer that are ready to be moved in and are available through resale. Each apartment covers a carpet area between 350 and 1180 sq. ft. The prices of the flats ranges from 16.8 to 56.6 lakhs. Various amenities have been planned within the community, for the benefit of the home owners. Some of these amenities are kids’ play area, rainwater harvesting, club house; landscaped gardens, 24X7security and power back up. The Lodha Group was established in 1980 and has pioneered the development of fifty four communities since then. Thirty of their properties are under construction currently. Some of these properties are in Thane west aside from Dombivali.A part of the Kalyan-Dombivali Municipal Corporation, Dombivali is located in Thane and is a part of suburban Mumbai. Several industrial parks such as Ambernath and Taloje MIDCs are located here. The KMDT operates buses to enhance its connectivity to other parts of the area.

The area is smoothly connected to other areas by local trains and this locality is 57.7 kilometres from the ChhatrapatiShivaji International Airport using the Eastern Express Highway. This locality has many well-known schools, colleges, hospitals, and banks.

Aarsh Avenue Mumbai is a residential project developed by Aarsh Group. It is located at Badlapur West in Mumbai. It offers 94 units comprising of 1 and 2BHK apartments with their size ranging from 595 to 1000 sq. ft. Aarsh Group is one of the highly esteemed realtors in and around Mumbai. The company’s main objective is to develop projects that are technologically advanced, with best quality infrastructure. The structural designs of their residential projects are of global standards. Mayuresh Enterprises Manohar Vikas is a residential complex in Badlapur West, near Navi Mumbai. The flats on offer are of 1, 2 and 3BHK configuration and priced between Rs 35.1 and 47.6 lakhs. These flats are ready for possession and available through the developer. There are 176 units in the complex, whose super built-up areas measure from 740 to 1270 sq. ft. Numerous amenities are there for home owners to use like club house, children’s play area, landscaped gardens, indoor games room and jogging track. Badlapur is located close to Navi Mumbai. It is 57.7 kilometers from the Mumbai International Airport. NMMT buses are an important mode of communication for the area.

Sun Nidhi Park, located in Nala Sopara, Mumbai, offers 1, 2 and 3 BHK apartments, with the price being on request. There are 168 units in total, and the apartment sizes range from 570 to 860 sq. ft. The amenities include gymnasium, swimming pool, children’s play area, club house, table tennis and pool table, multipurpose private lush green garden, health club, steam and sauna, private security arrangements, badminton court, etc. Situated in the Thane district of Maharashtra, Nala Sopara is well-connected to Mira Road and Mumbai through the Western Express highway. It also houses several reputed educational institutions, hospitals, shopping malls etc. The property rates in this area have risen by up to 23.8% in the last 6 months.
